categories: Category:Venator-class Star Destroyers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: A Venator-class Star Destroyer was used by the Galactic Empire during the early stage of its reign. It was present during the construction of the Death Star in orbit of Geonosis. The Star Destroyer lacked the red markings present on others of its kind used by the Galactic Republic.
The Venator-class Star Destroyer first appeared in the 2005 prequel trilogy film, Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith.
